data.description: Welcome to your new home! Gorgeous townhome with tons of light!  Upon entering, you see the gleaming wood floors, beautiful trim and an open floor plan. The kitchen overlooks the dining and family rooms. Plenty of counter space for cooking and entertaining! The upstairs boosts 2 bedrooms with a shared bath. The master has a a large closet space and a newly finished bath. The basement holds your 1 car garage and a large storage space. The front patio opens up to a green space between buildings. The community pool is a quick walk away. Kitchen appliances included. Amenities include clubhouse, pool, and play area. This home is ready for you to move right in!
